title: BCS Tools 2.06
description: The CODESYS-based software BCS Tools is IEC 61131-3 standard compliant, offering full connectivity and communication. Four versions of the programming software are available - Lite, Basic, Professional and Advanced. Lite offers a limited, free version of the product, while the Basic version covers the vast majority of requirements for the vast majority of customers. For customers with exceptional support needs and/or unlimited I/O requirements, we offer our Professional and Advanced versions to satisfy your more specialized customer demands
